00:00:01,680 --> 00:00:02,820
沒人相信愛麗絲
No one believed Alice

14
00:00:02,820 --> 00:00:05,670
所說的仙境冒險
when she spoke of her adventures in Wonderland,

15
00:00:05,680 --> 00:00:07,740
所以紅桃杰克和我帶她回去
so the Knave of Hearts and I brought her back

16
00:00:07,740 --> 00:00:09,110
尋找她的真愛
to search for her true love.

17
00:00:09,110 --> 00:00:10,940
他在這里  我能感覺到
He's here. I can feel it.

18
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:13,060
有人想阻止她
There are those who will try to stop her.

19
00:00:13,060 --> 00:00:14,980
讓那個女孩許下三個愿
What we want can't be accomplished

20
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:16,830
我們的目的才能達成
until the girl's made all her wishes.

21
00:00:16,890 --> 00:00:18,610
但是愛麗絲的偉大冒險
But Alice's greatest adventure

22
00:00:18,620 --> 00:00:19,890
剛剛開始
has just begun.

23
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,910
《仙境奇緣》前情提要
Previously in Wonderland...

24
00:00:21,910 --> 00:00:23,360
也許你能騙過所有人
Maybe you've fooled all these people,

25
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:24,830
但我知道你的真實身份
but I know who you really are.

26
00:00:24,830 --> 00:00:26,670
人們想要你死
People want you dead.

27
00:00:27,620 --> 00:00:28,560
我沒法動了
I can't move.

28
00:00:28,610 --> 00:00:29,870
愛麗絲  出什么事了
Alice, what's happening?

29
00:00:31,900 --> 00:00:32,800
安娜斯塔西婭
Anastasia!

30
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:36,930
你就打算跳進魔鏡嗎
So you're just going to jump through some magic mirror?

31
00:00:38,140 --> 00:00:40,890
我們可以為所欲為
We can be whoever we want to be.

32
00:00:41,170 --> 00:00:42,200
下一站  
Next stop...

33
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:43,510
仙境
Wonderland.

34
00:00:53,890 --> 00:00:55,350
你們在干什么
What are you doing?

35
00:00:55,580 --> 00:00:56,500
母親
Mother.

36
00:00:58,210 --> 00:00:59,080
你跟蹤我們到了這里嗎
Did you follow us here?

37
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:00,710
當然是
Damn right I did.

38
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:04,470
你要和這個廢柴
You're going to run off with this...

39
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:06,380
私奔嗎
loser?

40
00:01:07,380 --> 00:01:08,740
是這么回事嗎
Is that what's happening here?

41
00:01:08,740 --> 00:01:09,920
這不關你的事
It's none of your business.

42
00:01:09,920 --> 00:01:11,220
我生下了你  親愛的
I birthed you, dear.

43
00:01:12,170 --> 00:01:14,030
所以如果你打算毀掉你的生活
So if you are going to ruin your life,

44
00:01:14,030 --> 00:01:15,910
這當然和我有關
it absolutely is.

45
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,320
這不是毀掉  媽媽
It's not ruin, mom.

46
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:19,930
我找到了威爾
I found Will.

47
00:01:20,520 --> 00:01:21,580
我知道
I know.

48
00:01:22,930 --> 00:01:24,190
悲劇就在于此
That's the tragedy.

49
00:01:26,740 --> 00:01:28,580
我想讓女兒成為女王
I wanted a queen for a daughter,

50
00:01:28,660 --> 00:01:30,320
但結果她成了什么
but what did I get instead?

51
00:01:31,580 --> 00:01:32,720
一個失敗者
A failure.

52
00:01:33,300 --> 00:01:34,520
我終于
I'm happy...

53
00:01:34,930 --> 00:01:35,820
得到了快樂
finally.

54
00:01:35,820 --> 00:01:36,910
和他一起嗎
With him?

55
00:01:38,450 --> 00:01:40,290
我這一生
I did not spend my entire life

56
00:01:40,290 --> 00:01:42,280
都在拼命工作
working my fingers to the bone

57
00:01:42,440 --> 00:01:43,920
好讓你出人頭地
so that you could move up,

58
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:46,210
可不是為了讓你拋棄一切的
only to have you toss it all away.

59
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:49,000
顯然你不是當公主的料子
Obviously you're not princess material,

60
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:51,730
但我以為你至少也能搭上個貴族
but I thought you could at least land a nobleman.

61
00:01:52,770 --> 00:01:55,400
而不是他  小偷威爾·史卡利
Not him-- Will Scarlet, the thief.

62
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,980
我不是小偷  以后不是了
I'm no thief. Not anymore.

63
00:01:58,050 --> 00:02:00,000
他會給你什么樣的生活
What kind of a life is he going to give you?

64
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,780
他什么也不必給我
He doesn't need to give me anything.

65
00:02:03,650 --> 00:02:04,600
我愛他
I love him.

66
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:09,710
你沒法靠愛活著  安娜斯塔西婭
You cannot live on love, Anastasia.

67
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,770
當你以自己慘痛的經歷得到教訓時
And when you learn that lesson the hard way,

68
00:02:11,770 --> 00:02:14,440
你就會回到原點
you will be right back here where you started.

69
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,510
但你回來時  記得帶個桶子
But when you come back, bring a bucket.

70
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:21,950
因為你要進我家門的唯一方法
Because the only way you'll be coming back inside my house

71
00:02:22,670 --> 00:02:24,870
就是給我倒尿壺
is to empty my chamber pot.

72
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,510
那你們走吧
Off with you then.

73
00:02:30,320 --> 00:02:31,940
至少我還有你妹妹
At least I have your sisters.

74
00:02:32,870 --> 00:02:34,030
別聽她的
Don't listen to her.

75
00:02:34,740 --> 00:02:35,900
我會為我們建造新生活的
I'll build us a life--

76
00:02:35,900 --> 00:02:37,590
如果有必要  我會一點點堆砌
brick by brick if I have to.

77
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,720
我愛你
I love you...

78
00:02:40,350 --> 00:02:41,760
是因為真實的你
for who you truly are.

79
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,760
而不是我想讓你成為的人
Not for who I want you to be.

80
00:02:48,090 --> 00:02:49,030
來吧
Come on.

81
00:02:51,660 --> 00:02:52,830
再見了  媽媽
Good-bye, mom.

82
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:50,090
給你披上
There you go...

83
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:54,050
遮擋雨水和雪花  或者
in case of rain or snow or...

84
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:56,440
天上掉下的任何東西
anything that might fall from the sky.

85
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:06,960
真對不起  威爾
I'm so sorry, Will.

86
00:04:08,430 --> 00:04:09,960
如果我沒有逼你許下那個愿望
If I hadn't bribed you with that wish,

87
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,270
你就不會...
you would have never...

88
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:17,120
塞勒斯總說愿望是有代價的
Cyrus always said they had consequences.

89
00:04:18,310 --> 00:04:19,740
現在我明白了
Now I understand.

90
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:23,030
我會解救你的
I will get you out of this.

91
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:25,860
如果我能找到塞勒斯  那我們一起就能...
If I can find Cyrus, then together we can...

92
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,390
我在騙誰呢
Who am I fooling?

93
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,080
我都不知道他在哪里
I don't even know where he is.

94
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,940
我知道  好消息吧  親愛的
Then it's a good thing I do, darling.

95
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:40,450
也許我們能互相幫助
Perhaps we can help one another.

96
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:42,480
我為什么要幫你
Why would I do anything to help you?

97
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:44,440
當時機合適時  人們愿意做什么
You'd be surprised what people are willing to do

98
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:46,300
會讓你大吃一驚的
when the right circumstances present themselves.

99
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:49,800
你開不出夠好的條件讓我...
There's not a circumstance you could present that would ever...

100
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,060
連找到
Not even finding out

101
00:04:51,060 --> 00:04:53,230
你親愛的精靈的關押地也不算嗎
where your precious genie is being held?

102
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,770
是啊
Yes.

103
00:04:56,740 --> 00:04:58,980
你不如放低點姿態
So why don't you get down off your high horse,

104
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,380
我們來做筆交易
and we can make a deal?

105
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:04,190
什么交易
What sort of a deal?

106
00:05:04,190 --> 00:05:07,170
這筆交易能解決我倆都有的一個問題
The sort of deal to handle the one problem we both share--

107
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:08,930
賈法爾
Jafar.

108
00:05:09,990 --> 00:05:11,490
你們在合作
You're working together.

109
00:05:11,590 --> 00:05:13,180
他怎么是你的問題了
How is he a problem for you?

110
00:05:13,180 --> 00:05:15,480
他只不過是我達到目的的手段  親愛的
Well, he's simply a means to an end, darling.

111
00:05:16,330 --> 00:05:18,160
但當目的達成時  我得保證
But when that end comes, I need to ensure

112
00:05:18,160 --> 00:05:20,330
我有能力保護自己
I have the power to protect myself.

113
00:05:21,950 --> 00:05:23,440
我可不想和你朋友下場一樣
Wouldn't want to end up like your friend here,

114
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,590
對吧
now would we?

115
00:05:29,260 --> 00:05:31,200
他也是你的朋友  曾經是
He was your friend, too, once.

116
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:35,350
據我所知  不止是個朋友
More than a friend, from what I gather.

117
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:39,140
或者他也只是你達到目的的手段
Or was he just a means to an end as well?

118
00:05:40,330 --> 00:05:41,490
那就是你的問題  愛麗絲
That's your problem, Alice--

119
00:05:41,490 --> 00:05:43,700
當你該考慮未來時
always dwelling on the past,

120
00:05:44,210 --> 00:05:46,590
卻總是沉湎于過去
when really you should be thinking about the future.

121
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:49,050
你到底想讓我做什么
What exactly is it you want me to do?

122
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:50,680
幫我弄點東西
Help me procure something.

123
00:05:51,350 --> 00:05:54,010
就是一點粉末狀的魔法
Just a little bit of magic in the form of dust.

124
00:05:54,210 --> 00:05:56,010
大概一日路程
It's about a day's journey away.

125
00:05:57,260 --> 00:05:59,670
這能保護我免受黑魔法的傷害
And it's going to protect me against dark magic

126
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:01,350
比如賈法爾那種
such as Jafar's.

127
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:05,110
你這么想要的話  自己去取
If you want it so badly, get it yourself.

128
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,580
我也想  親愛的
I would, darling,

129
00:06:06,940 --> 00:06:08,550
但這么強大的東西到現在還原封未動
but there's a reason something so powerful

130
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:09,890
是有原因的
sits untouched.

131
00:06:10,490 --> 00:06:12,990
要得到它  對多數人來說簡直是尋死
Retrieving it, for most, is a suicide mission.

132
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,150
而你認為我會就這么答應以身犯險
And you think I'll just agree to risk my life?

133
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:19,730
不  至少得給你點好處
No. No, not unless you're properly compensated.

134
00:06:22,450 --> 00:06:24,660
所以我提出這項交易
Which is why I propose a trade.

135
00:06:25,630 --> 00:06:27,240
你把魔塵給我弄來
You get me the dust,

136
00:06:27,940 --> 00:06:29,880
我就幫你找你的精靈
and I'll help you find your genie.

137
00:06:30,390 --> 00:06:32,370
我自己會找  謝了
I'll find him myself, thank you.

138
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:34,600
可你不知道上哪找
Not if you don't know where you're looking.

139
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:39,130
賈法爾的塔以魔法隱匿
Jafar's tower is hidden, enshrouded by magic.

140
00:06:39,570 --> 00:06:41,150
沒有我的話  你即使站在塔前
You could be standing right in front of it,

141
00:06:41,150 --> 00:06:43,270
也毫不知情
not knowing it's there, without my help.

142
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:48,320
你想找到塞勒斯  我是你最好的機會
If you want to find Cyrus, then I am your best bet--

143
00:06:48,790 --> 00:06:50,440
也是唯一的機會
Your only bet, actually.

144
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:19,160
他們對你做了什么
What did they do to you?

145
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:21,420
今天
Today...

146
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:24,300
是巨石
it was the giant rocks.

147
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:27,000
有些甚至跟人一樣大
Some of them as large as a man.

148
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,760
他逼我把石頭
He makes me move them

149
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,870
從石梯底部搬到頂部
from the bottom of the stone staircase to the top.

150
00:07:32,430 --> 00:07:33,660
為什么
For what purpose?

151
00:07:34,560 --> 00:07:35,530
沒理由
None.

152
00:07:35,890 --> 00:07:37,480
那他為什么把你關在這里
Well, then why does he keep you here?

153
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,380
跟你一樣
Like you...

154
00:07:40,020 --> 00:07:42,120
我身上有他想要的東西
I have something he wants.

155
00:07:42,960 --> 00:07:43,970
是什么
Which is what?

156
00:07:44,030 --> 00:07:45,310
無所謂
Doesn't matter.

157
00:07:46,910 --> 00:07:49,320
因為他永遠都得不到
Because it's something he will never get.

158
00:07:51,290 --> 00:07:53,500
所以我將繼續被他懲罰
And so my punishment continues.

159
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:55,200
不會很久了  老先生
Well, not for long, old man.

160
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:04,610
因為今天就是我們離開這里的日子
Because today's the day we get out of here.

161
00:08:19,570 --> 00:08:21,050
你確定是這里嗎
Are you sure this is the spot?

162
00:08:21,740 --> 00:08:24,230
我一顆漿果都沒看到  我快餓死了
I've not seen a single berry, and I'm bloody starving.

163
00:08:24,230 --> 00:08:26,660
上周這里還有很多呢
Yeah, there was a bunch here last week.

164
00:08:26,900 --> 00:08:28,060
我們那天捕到的魚呢
What about that fish we caught the other day?

165
00:08:28,060 --> 00:08:30,010
-還有剩的嗎  -沒了
- We got any of that left? - No...

166
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:31,270
只剩骨頭了
Just the bones.

167
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:33,630
可以把魚骨在水里浸久一點
We could soak 'em in water long enough...

168
00:08:33,630 --> 00:08:35,110
那就是湯了
and call it soup.

169
00:08:36,060 --> 00:08:38,220
天哪  快看啊
Bloody hell, will you look at that?

170
00:08:39,260 --> 00:08:41,120
這個可以燉出靚湯
This'll make a right fine stew.

171
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:46,800
別碰
Ah! No! Don't!

172
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:49,130
這蘑菇會把你變大
Those are the mushrooms that make you grow big.

173
00:08:49,700 --> 00:08:51,540
現在這馬車都快坐不下了
We can barely fit in the wagon as it is.

174
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,800
馬車太小了嗎
The wagon too small for ya?

175
00:08:54,590 --> 00:08:55,910
當然不是
No, of course not.

176
00:08:57,570 --> 00:08:58,720
我們只要這樣的就行
It's all we need.

177
00:08:59,310 --> 00:09:01,700
抱歉  親愛的  我已經盡力了
I'm sorry, luv. I am doing the best I can.

178
00:09:01,930 --> 00:09:02,940
我知道
I know.

179
00:09:03,660 --> 00:09:05,440
我只是以為這里一切會有所不同
I just thought things would be different here.

180
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:08,070
我第一次聽聞仙境時
When I first heard about Wonderland,

181
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:11,190
以為這里會奇妙美好
I figured that the "wonder" was short for "wonderful",

182
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,890
而不是日日擔心怎么過活
not "wonder how we're gonna make it?"

183
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:15,560
我愛你
Well, I love ya.

184
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:17,810
我保證  我們會撐過去的
And I promise ya, we will make it.

185
00:09:26,850 --> 00:09:30,380
那些面包聞起來太香了
Ahh! Smell that bread, it smells heavenly.

186
00:09:31,490 --> 00:09:32,800
能給我們一塊嗎  伙計
Can you spare a loaf, mate?

187
00:09:33,140 --> 00:09:34,910
不行  這是貢品
Can't. It's for the palace.

188
00:09:34,910 --> 00:09:37,540
宮里要辦舞會  連面包屑都得端上
There's to be a ball, and every crumb's spoken for.

189
00:09:39,230 --> 00:09:40,380
真是謝謝了
Well, thanks a lot then.

