uh... what do you want?

260
00:13:30,740 --> 00:13:32,720
兔子  你引起了我的注意
I'm intrigued by you, Rabbit.

261
00:13:32,720 --> 00:13:35,660
不是要把我當主食吃掉的那種吧
Not in a-a main course kind of way, I hope?

262
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:38,160
大可安心  你還沒有拿來煮的價值
Rest easy, you're far too valuable to cook.

263
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:39,790
真是松了一口氣
Oh, what a relief.

264
00:13:39,790 --> 00:13:42,310
我感興趣的是為何一個認識愛麗絲那么久的人
I'm interested why someone who's known Alice for so long

265
00:13:42,310 --> 00:13:44,530
還會如此深深地背叛她
would betray her so deeply.

266
00:13:44,540 --> 00:13:46,800
我認識她的時間并不長
I, uh, haven't known her that long.

267
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:49,100
最多是個熟人而已
I'm more of an acquaintance, really.

268
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,360
你有困難
You have a problem,

269
00:13:53,630 --> 00:13:55,330
