All that I require in exchange is that you help me.

272
00:14:02,890 --> 00:14:03,940
以什么來幫你
With what?

273
00:14:04,090 --> 00:14:05,170
愛麗絲
Alice.

274
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,610
從她還是小女孩起  你就認識她了
You've known her since she was a girl.

275
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:11,030
