不
No!

283
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,550
在找我嗎
You looking for me?

284
00:16:06,920 --> 00:16:08,420
我還沒見過這個地方
I haven't seen this place.

285
00:16:08,730 --> 00:16:10,750
很少有人見過之后  還能活著講這個故事
Few have and lived to tell the tale.

286
00:16:11,980 --> 00:16:12,920
真會安慰人
Comforting.

287
00:16:14,760 --> 00:16:15,570
那么
Well, then...

288
00:16:15,810 --> 00:16:17,780
魔塵到底在哪里
where exactly is this magic dust?

289
00:16:19,350 --> 00:16:20,210
就在那邊
Over there.

290
00:16:24,060 --> 00:16:25,440
越過這峽谷嗎
Across the ravine?

291
00:16:27,430 --> 00:16:29,980
-我想這里沒有橋或  -恐怕沒有
- I don't suppose there's a bridge or-- - Afraid not.

292
00:16:30,650 --> 00:16:31,820
那你的魔法呢
And your magic?

293
00:16:33,650 --> 00:16:35,600
親愛的  如果我能自己拿到的話
Darling, if I could have gotten it myself,

294
00:16:35,600 --> 00:16:37,120
你不認為我現在就能到手了嗎
don't you think I would have by now?

295
00:16:38,220 --> 00:16:40,010
也許不可能拿得到
Maybe it's impossible.

296
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,700
當然不是每個人都能
Not for everyone.

297
