301
00:16:56,910 --> 00:16:58,290
但是在我們倆當中
But between the two of us,

302
00:16:58,290 --> 00:16:59,990
我覺得你成功的可能性比我大
I like your chances better than mine.

303
00:17:00,210 --> 00:17:02,040
親愛的  我有很多東西
I am many things, darling,

304
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:04,260
但是沒有純潔的心靈
But pure of heart is not one of them.

305
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:10,680
看看這里
Look here.

306
00:17:11,550 --> 00:17:14,000
甚至比我想象中的還要漂亮
It's even more beautiful than I imagined.

307
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:18,250
