Me trousers feel like they're on backwards.

308
00:17:19,990 --> 00:17:22,910
不要在扭來扭去了  大家都在看呢
Stop squirming, will you? People are looking.

309
00:17:23,210 --> 00:17:24,860
那是因為我們不屬于這里  安娜
That's 'cause we don't belong here, Anna.

310
00:17:25,630 --> 00:17:27,590
這一刻  想象一下我們屬于這里
Just for a moment, imagine we do.

311
00:17:28,390 --> 00:17:30,320
如果我們相信  他們也會相信
If we believe it... so will they.

312
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:35,220
瞧瞧那些吃的
Look at all that food.

313
00:17:36,260 --> 00:17:37,360
就這樣浪費實在太遺憾了
It would be a shame to let it go to waste.

314
00:17:37,360 --> 00:17:38,200
你來嗎
Are you coming?

315
00:17:39,290 --> 00:17:40,120
等一會吧
In a moment.

