真的
Indeed.

332
00:18:39,410 --> 00:18:41,640
我必須承認  我覺得他們
I must confess, I find them...

333
00:18:42,270 --> 00:18:42,990
很無聊
boring.

334
00:18:43,780 --> 00:18:45,820
我非常想換個環境
I'm desperate for a change of scenery.

335
00:18:47,580 --> 00:18:48,380
是的
Yes.

336
00:18:49,960 --> 00:18:51,120
我知道這種感覺
Yes, I know the feeling.

337
00:18:54,290 --> 00:18:56,470
我知道每個在我王宮里的貴婦人
I know every lady in my court.

338
00:18:58,110 --> 00:18:59,950
可為什么我以前從未見過你
Why haven't I seen you before?

339
00:19:00,590 --> 00:19:01,570
我想
I'd say...

340
00:19:02,060 --> 00:19:03,920
不是你還沒看仔細
either you haven't been looking hard enough...

341
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:07,100
就是也許我不是位貴婦人
or maybe I'm no lady.

342
