00:34:17,050 --> 00:34:19,110
你不能永遠寄望于這些愿望
Can't hold onto those wishes forever...

574
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:22,260
也不能寄望與塞勒斯重逢
or the hope of seeing Cyrus again.

575
00:34:35,500 --> 00:34:37,420
我會和他重逢的
I will see him again.

576
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:41,110
你聽見了嗎
Did you hear that?

577
00:34:44,010 --> 00:34:46,360
如果有人逃走  賈法爾會要了我們的命
Jafar will have our heads if anyone gets away.

578
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:47,780
我們去看看
Let's go have a look.

579
00:35:02,920 --> 00:35:03,980
謝謝你  兔子
Thank you, rabbit.

580
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:05,680
這的確對我很有用
I actually think that was helpful.

581
00:35:05,930 --> 00:35:07,470
那我可以走了嗎 
Uh, can I leave now?

582
00:35:07,470 --> 00:35:08,360
還不行
Not quite.

583
00:35:08,550 --> 00:35:09,680
但我已經把所有事都告訴你了
But I've told you everything.

584
00:35:09,740 --> 00:35:11,070
我也許不需要你再說什么了
There might not be more to say,

585
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:12,610
但還有很多事需要你去做
But there's certainly more to do.

586
00:35:14,270 --> 00:35:15,980
現在我想出去走走
I'd like to take a trip now.

587
00:35:15,980 --> 00:35:17,590
你可以坐著魔毯去
Well, you've got your carpet.

588
00:35:17,590 --> 00:35:20,410
我想去的地方  只有你能帶我去
Where I want to go is a place only you can take me.

589
00:35:22,600 --> 00:35:23,620
開始挖洞
Start digging.

590
00:35:23,620 --> 00:35:25,520
賈法爾  我不能就這么走了
Jafar, I can't just leave.

591
00:35:25,520 --> 00:35:27,390
皇后會察覺到的  然后...
The queen will know something is wrong, a-and then--

592
00:35:27,390 --> 00:35:29,390
現在你為我做事  兔子
You work for me now, rabbit.

593
00:35:29,950 --> 00:35:32,290
還是你需要我再提醒一下你
Or do I really need to remind you?

594
00:35:36,390 --> 00:35:37,690
兔子
Rabbit!

595
00:35:40,160 --> 00:35:41,050
兔子
Rabbit!

596
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:45,170
兔子
Rabbit!

597
00:35:45,840 --> 00:35:46,970
求你  別叫
Please don't.

598
00:35:49,240 --> 00:35:50,250
兔子
Rabbit!

599
00:35:50,570 --> 00:35:51,450
快走
Just go.

600
00:35:52,090 --> 00:35:52,590
什么
What?

601
00:35:52,590 --> 00:35:54,540
去找她  快走
Find her. Go!

602
00:36:01,480 --> 00:36:02,410
兔子
Rabbit!

603
00:36:06,430 --> 00:36:09,210
我知道反抗你是沒用的  賈法爾
I know it's futile to resist you, Jafar.

604
00:36:09,630 --> 00:36:11,100
我會遵照你的指示
I'll do what you ask.

605
00:36:11,600 --> 00:36:12,920
你做對了
You made the right choice.

606
00:36:13,670 --> 00:36:16,020
即使找到出路逃出這座塔
Even if you did find your way out of the tower,

607
00:36:16,640 --> 00:36:18,620
你也沒辦法逃出塔外之物的魔爪
There's no escaping what's beyond it.

608
00:36:18,620 --> 00:36:20,250
這是什么意思
What does that mean?

609
00:36:20,250 --> 00:36:22,110
你應該慶幸你沒有去親身體驗
Just be glad you didn't find out.

610
00:36:22,710 --> 00:36:24,010
開始挖洞吧
Now dig your hole.

611
00:36:24,830 --> 00:36:26,000
去哪
Where to?

612
00:36:26,540 --> 00:36:27,570
你知道去哪
You know where.

613
00:36:55,250 --> 00:36:57,340
溜進我的舞會是一回事
Sneaking into my ball was one thing.

614
00:36:57,590 --> 00:36:59,780
我倒是很欣賞你的大膽
I rather admire the boldness of it.

615
00:37:00,650 --> 00:37:02,330
但偷我東西就另當別論了
But stealing from me?

616
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:04,250
為什么要這樣
What possessed you?

617
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:06,680
這有關系嗎
Does it matter?

618
00:37:06,680 --> 00:37:07,430
有關系
It might.

619
00:37:09,240 --> 00:37:11,140
在這片國土上  您比任何人都要富有
You have more wealth than anyone in the realm.

620
00:37:11,670 --> 00:37:13,070
丟了也不會在意
You'll hardly miss it.

621
00:37:18,710 --> 00:37:20,200
我比您更需要它們
I need it more than you do.

622
00:37:20,200 --> 00:37:22,400
一個農婦要珠寶來做什么
What does a peasant need with jewels?

623
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:23,560
一個國王要珠寶來做什么
What does a king need with them?

624
00:37:23,560 --> 00:37:25,220
親愛的  現實就是如此
That, my dear, is the way it goes.

625
00:37:26,000 --> 00:37:28,610
我的世界充滿了財富
My world... filled with wealth,

626
00:37:28,610 --> 00:37:29,610
而你的世界...
And yours...

627
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,300
充滿了對財富的渴求
filled with longing.

628
00:37:33,540 --> 00:37:36,300
通常  我們的世界是沒有交集的
Generally, our realms don't meet.

629
00:37:38,570 --> 00:37:39,740
您抓住了我
You caught me.

630
00:37:43,710 --> 00:37:45,160
我的命運將會如何
What will my fate be?

631
00:37:45,400 --> 00:37:46,710
這取決于你
That depends on you.

632
00:37:47,600 --> 00:37:49,400
小姑娘  你現在的世界
Ah, there's something about you, girl.

633
00:37:52,100 --> 00:37:53,180
你現在的生活
The life you're in,

634
00:37:54,290 --> 00:37:56,670
并不是你應該過的生活  對嗎
It isn't the one you were meant for, is it?

635
00:37:56,670 --> 00:37:57,950
我就只需要這些
It's all I need.

636
00:37:58,430 --> 00:37:59,890
那你為何還要偷盜
Then why are you stealing?

637
00:38:05,580 --> 00:38:08,200
如果你不需要偷盜珠寶
What if instead of stealing these jewels,

638
00:38:08,200 --> 00:38:12,450
而單純的擁有它們呢
they simply... belonged to you?

639
00:38:13,750 --> 00:38:14,830
您會把它們送給我嗎
You'll give them to me?

640
00:38:14,830 --> 00:38:15,650
也許會
Perhaps.

641
00:38:17,090 --> 00:38:18,380
有何代價
At what price?

642
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,120
執子之手
Your hand,

643
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:24,340
與子偕老
in marriage.

644
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:29,600
我一直在找一個皇后
I have been searching for a queen.

645
00:38:31,450 --> 00:38:32,920
而你完全符合要求
And you fit the bill.

646
00:38:47,580 --> 00:38:48,650
你所有的...
What you have...

647
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,650
遠遠不止是美貌
Goes far beyond your beauty.

648
00:38:51,650 --> 00:38:54,260
你的品質極其令人難以琢磨
What you have is what is most elusive--

649
00:38:54,890 --> 00:38:57,830
你的追求遠超能力范圍的事物
The drive to be more than you are.

650
00:38:58,900 --> 00:39:02,260
這正是統治之道
That is how one rules.

651
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,740
這也是...
And that...

652
00:39:07,260 --> 00:39:10,080
我渴望擁有的力量
is what I desire at my side.

653
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:13,550
如果我愛的是其他人呢
What if I love another?

654
00:39:13,830 --> 00:39:16,070
我知道  舞會上的那個小伙
Yes, the fellow from the ball.

655
00:39:17,240 --> 00:39:20,320
愛情是神圣的
Love is a noble thing.

656
00:39:21,400 --> 00:39:23,510
但它能支持你們多久
But how far will it get you, hmm?

657
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:25,020
假設你賣掉它
Let's say you sell this.

658
00:39:25,710 --> 00:39:26,960
得到的錢又能讓你們
How long would it last you before you're

659
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:28,480
揮霍多久
right back where you started?

660
00:39:28,920 --> 00:39:31,130
而不久之后你就會意識到
And that love you cling to,

661
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:36,080
你所不離不棄的愛情是不夠的
It won't be long before you realize, it's not enough.

662
00:39:37,560 --> 00:39:38,370
接下來
And then?

663
00:39:38,710 --> 00:39:40,820
接下來  親愛的  就太晚了
And then, my dear, it will be too late for you.

664
00:39:45,330 --> 00:39:47,180
快點  快點
Come on, come on.

665
00:39:59,610 --> 00:40:01,070
仙境的人民們
People of wonderland,

666
00:40:02,350 --> 00:40:03,440
容我向你們介紹
I give you...

667
00:40:03,890 --> 00:40:04,640
你們的皇后
Your queen.

668
00:40:14,180 --> 00:40:15,300
安娜斯塔西婭
Anastasia.

669
00:40:54,640 --> 00:40:55,690
對不起
I'm sorry.

670
00:41:52,610 --> 00:41:53,720
很好  塞勒斯
All right, cyrus.

671
00:41:54,710 --> 00:41:56,540
我知道你就在這附近
I know you're out there somewhere.

672
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,170
指路吧
Now show me.

673
00:42:25,620 --> 00:42:26,800
我來找你了
I'm coming for you.

674
00:42:40,120 --> 00:42:41,720
愛麗絲  我來找你了
Alice, I'm coming for you.

